Reasoning: 
1. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper deals with the end-to-end performance of wireless communication systems, which is a core topic in information theory. 
2. cs.COMM (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper discusses the performance of wireless communication systems, which is a key aspect of networking and internet architecture. 
3. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper deals with wireless communication systems, which is a subfield of networking and internet architecture. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper discusses the performance of a system (wireless communication system), which is a topic in systems and control. 
5. cs.PE (Performance) - The paper focuses on the performance of wireless communication systems, which is a subfield of performance evaluation.
